nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/MarilynManson-EvanRachelWood-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marilyn-manson" target="_blank" rel="noopener">玛丽莲·曼森</a>撤销了对埃文·雷切尔·伍德提起的诽谤诉讼。</p><p> 2022 年，这位备受争议的摇滚歌手（真名布莱恩·华纳） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sues-evan-rachel-wood-for-defamation-3173472">对这位演员采取了法律行动</a>，后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">公开指控她的前伴侣曼森</a>虐待她，声称他在她十几岁的时候就开始为她打扮，并“多年来对我进行了可怕的虐待” 。</p><p>华纳<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-denies-abuse-allegations-calls-recent-claims-horrible-distortions-of-reality-2870187">否认了所有指控</a>，并在诉讼中声称伍德“招募、协调并迫使”女性对这位音乐家做出虚假陈述。伍德<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-responds-marilyn-manson-defamation-lawsuit-3182521">当时回应说，她“并不害怕”</a>曼森的诽谤诉讼，并补充说“这是让幸存者保持沉默的报复的一部分”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-defamation-case-against-evan-rachel-wood-mostly-dismissed-by-us-judge-3441811">该案的关键主张于去年5月被驳回</a>。</p><p>八月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-accuses-evan-rachel-wood-of-forging-a-letter-to-the-fbi-3788772">华纳在针对伍德的新诉讼中声称</a>，她伪造了联邦调查局一名真正特工的信件，以此来抹黑他的形象。</p><p>昨天， <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/marilyn-manson-drops-defamation-lawsuit-evan-rachel-wood-1235182106/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>报道华纳已经放弃了诉讼和任何相关上诉。根据法律文件，华纳已同意向伍德支付近32.7万美元的律师费。</p><p>在<em>《滚石》杂志的一份声明中，</em>伍德的一名代表称华纳的诉讼是“一场宣传噱头”，其目的是“破坏他众多指控者的可信度并重振他摇摇欲坠的职业生涯”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3579557" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3579557" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3579557" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3579557" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽莲·曼森和埃文·蕾切尔·伍德，2006 年。（约翰·希勒/WireImage/Getty Images 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p> “但他试图压制和恐吓伍德女士的努力失败了，”伍德的代表继续说道。 “正如初审法院正确认定的那样，华纳的主张毫无根据。华纳决定最终放弃诉讼并向伍德女士支付近 327,000 美元的全额费用赔偿金，这也证实了这一点。”</p><p>上个月（10月9日），洛杉矶检察官透露，针对华纳的性虐待案有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sexual-abuse-case-new-leads-evidence-3801970">“新线索和额外证据”</a>需要追查。</p><p>洛杉矶县地方检察官乔治·加斯科恩在一份新闻声明中表示：“高级工作人员已经会见了受害者，我们的检察官在整个过程中继续与受害者及其代表保持联系。”</p><p>在发表声明之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/game-of-thrones-star-esme-bianco-hits-out-at-la-prosecutor-over-mishandled-marilyn-manson-rape-allegations-3801830"><i>《权力的游戏》</i>主演埃斯梅·比安科猛烈抨击加斯科尼，称其对华纳的强奸指控“处理不当”</a> 。</p><p>她说，过去四年等待检察官对指控做出决定是“绝对的痛苦”，并补充说她不得不“追捕”地方检察官办公室以获取最新情况。</p><p> 2021年，比安科<i> </i><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/game-of-thrones-actress-esme-bianco-accuses-marilyn-manson-of-abuse-i-felt-like-a-prisoner-2877873">公开指控</a>华纳，声称这位歌手涉嫌虐待（发生在 2009 年至 2011 年间）让她“[感觉]像个囚犯”。几个月后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/game-of-thrones-esme-bianco-files-lawsuit-against-marilyn-manson-2931423">这位女演员正式对华纳及其公司玛丽莲·曼森唱片公司提起诉讼。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3376385" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3376385" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3376385" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Esme-Bianco-from-Game-of-Thrones.jpeg" alt="" width="2000" height="1275" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Esme-Bianco-from-Game-of-Thrones.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Esme-Bianco-from-Game-of-Thrones-400x255.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Esme-Bianco-from-Game-of-Thrones-800x510.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Esme-Bianco-from-Game-of-Thrones-696x444.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Esme-Bianco-from-Game-of-Thrones-1392x887.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Esme-Bianco-from-Game-of-Thrones-1068x681.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3376385" class="wp-caption-text"> 《权力的游戏》中的埃斯梅·比安科。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>该诉讼指控性侵犯、身体虐待和人口贩卖。华纳否认了所有指控，称这些指控<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-denies-abuse-allegations-calls-recent-claims-horrible-distortions-of-reality-2870187">“对现实的可怕扭曲”</a> 。</p><p> 2023年1月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/games-of-thrones-actor-esme-bianco-and-marilyn-manson-reach-settlement-in-sexual-assault-lawsuit-3386310">诉讼被撤销</a>，双方达成庭外和解。该协议的具体条款尚不清楚。</p><p>然而，大约在她提起诉讼的同时，洛杉矶警方对几名女性的指控<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-county-sheriffs-department-investigate-marilyn-manson-abuse-claims-2883838">展开刑事调查</a>，其中包括比安科和演员埃文·雷切尔·伍德（华纳的前伴侣）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">她们指控华纳性虐待、诱骗和操纵</a>。 2022年9月，案件被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sexual-abuse-case-filed-with-los-angeles-district-attorneys-office-3314160">提交给洛杉矶县地方检察官办公室</a>。</p><p><b>如需有关英国性骚扰、攻击和强奸的帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问</b><a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/"><b>强奸危机慈善网站</b></a><b>。在美国，请访问</b><a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php"><b>RAINN</b></a> <b>。</b></p><p> <a href="https://